<fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/us/">Trending in the United States</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 02:30:46 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 02:30:46 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Michelle L. Price, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/23/at-dnc-gabrielle-giffords-joins-survivors-of-gun-violence-and-families-of-those-killed-in-shootings.webp" alt="At DNC, Gabrielle Giffords joins survivors of gun violence and families of those killed in shootings" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">At DNC, Gabrielle Giffords joins survivors of gun violence and families of those killed in shootings</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Survivors and family members of victims of gun violence gave a powerful attestation at the Democratic National Convention on Thursday to the ways shootings impacted their lives and spurred them to advocacy.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/23/at-dnc-gabrielle-giffords-joins-survivors-of-gun-violence-and-families-of-those-killed-in-shootings/"  >(Michelle L. Price, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:27:44 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:27:44 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jeff Arnold, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/22/trump-ends-border-interview-citing-safety-concerns-amid-search-for-death-threat-suspect.webp" alt="Trump ends border interview citing safety concerns amid search for death threat suspect" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump ends border interview citing safety concerns amid search for death threat suspect</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former President Donald Trump was whisked away from a NewsNation interview when he was told that things were not safe
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/22/trump-ends-border-interview-citing-safety-concerns-amid-search-for-death-threat-suspect/"  >(Jeff Arnold, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:34:49 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:34:49 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Eileen Lehpamer, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/21/fda-approves-potentially-life-saving-gel-designed-to-stop-bleeding-on-contact.webp" alt="FDA approves potentially life-saving gel designed to stop bleeding on contact" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">FDA approves potentially life-saving gel designed to stop bleeding on contact</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A New York-based company now has the green light to sell a potentially life-saving gel that stops bleeding on contact.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/21/fda-approves-potentially-life-saving-gel-designed-to-stop-bleeding-on-contact/"  >(Eileen Lehpamer, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:15:17 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:15:17 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Bill Disbrow, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/21/walz-bill-clinton-to-headline-night-3-of-dnc.webp" alt="Tim Walz accepts Democratic VP nomination on DNC's third night" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tim Walz accepts Democratic VP nomination on DNC's third night</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz accepted his party's nomination for vice president at the Democratic National Convention in Chicago on Wednesday and made the case that he's ready to win the 2024 race alongside his running mate, Vice President Kamala Harris.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/21/walz-bill-clinton-to-headline-night-3-of-dnc/"  >(Bill Disbrow, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:50:06 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:50:06 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Juan Cisneros, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/21/shein-sues-temu-alleging-copyright-infringement-and-fraud.webp" alt="Shein sues Temu alleging copyright infringement and fraud" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Shein sues Temu alleging copyright infringement and fraud</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Chinese owned fast-fashion brand Shein is suing rival Temu on allegations of copyright infringement, fraud and theft of trade secrets.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/21/shein-sues-temu-alleging-copyright-infringement-and-fraud/"  >(Juan Cisneros, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:57:36 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:57:36 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Niall Stanage, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/22/walz-caps-off-emotional-night-5-takeaways-from-day-3-of-dnc.webp" alt="Walz caps off emotional night: 5 takeaways from Day 3 of Democratic convention" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Walz caps off emotional night: 5 takeaways from Day 3 of Democratic convention</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The third day of the Democratic National Convention did not quite reach the emotional intensity of the previous two nights, but it kept the party’s momentum going ahead of Vice President Harris’s big speech on Thursday. Harris’s vice presidential nominee, Minnesota Gov.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/22/walz-caps-off-emotional-night-5-takeaways-from-day-3-of-dnc/"  >(Niall Stanage, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 04:05:22 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 04:05:22 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="GLENN GAMBOA and THALIA BEATY, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/23/with-their-massive-resources-corporations-could-be-champions-of-racial-equity-but-often-waiver.webp" alt="With their massive resources, corporations could be champions of racial equity but often waiver" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">With their massive resources, corporations could be champions of racial equity but often waiver</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (AP) — Forward Through Ferguson has made its mark on its community and the St. Louis region by focusing on justice and education, racial equity and policing reform.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/23/with-their-massive-resources-corporations-could-be-champions-of-racial-equity-but-often-waiver/"  >(GLENN GAMBOA and THALIA BEATY, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/world/">Around the world</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:47:13 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:47:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MONIKA SCISLOWSKA, Associated Press, KREX 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/23/indias-modi-holds-security-and-trade-talks-with-polands-leaders-en-route-to-war-torn-ukraine.webp" alt="India's Modi urges efforts to end Ukraine war after talks in Poland" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">India's Modi urges efforts to end Ukraine war after talks in Poland</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WARSAW, Poland (AP) — Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi urged diplomatic efforts to end the war in Ukraine during a visit to Poland on Thursday, pledging India's support and saying that no conflict can be solved on a battlefield.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/23/indias-modi-holds-security-and-trade-talks-with-polands-leaders-en-route-to-war-torn-ukraine/"  >(MONIKA SCISLOWSKA, Associated Press, KREX 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 21:43:36 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 21:43:36 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/20/queen-elizabeth-trump-book.webp" alt="Queen Elizabeth says Trump was 'very rude,' book claims" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Queen Elizabeth says Trump was 'very rude,' book claims</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Queen Elizabeth II found former President Trump “very rude,” according to a forthcoming biography about the late monarch that was previewed on Monday in the Daily Mail.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/20/queen-elizabeth-trump-book/"  >(Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:14:12 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 17:14:12 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/20/ancient-treasure-dating-back-thousands-years-unearthed-burial-mound.webp" alt="Ancient treasure dating back thousands of years unearthed in burial mound" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ancient treasure dating back thousands of years unearthed in burial mound</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A recent discovery made in a 2,000-year-old burial site in Kazakhstan shed light on the mysterious Kangyu Era. The findings included gold jewelry and a bronze mirror.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/20/ancient-treasure-dating-back-thousands-years-unearthed-burial-mound/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:10:18 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:10:18 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/20/spanish-woman-believed-to-be-the-oldest-person-in-the-world-has-died-at-age-117.webp" alt="Woman believed to be the oldest person in the world dies at 117" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Woman believed to be the oldest person in the world dies at 117</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      “Maria Branyas has left us. She has gone the way she wanted: in her sleep, at peace, and without pain.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/20/spanish-woman-believed-to-be-the-oldest-person-in-the-world-has-died-at-age-117/"  >(Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:57:22 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 00:57:22 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, PIX 11">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/23/rescuers-recover-fifth-body-from-sunken-superyacht-off-sicily-1-still-missing.webp" alt="Body of British tech magnate Mike Lynch is among those recovered from yacht wreckage, officials say" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Body of British tech magnate Mike Lynch is among those recovered from yacht wreckage, officials say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PORTICELLO, Sicily (AP) — The Italian coast guard said Thursday the body of British tech magnate Mike Lynch is among those recovered off the coast of Sicily from the wreckage of a superyacht whose builders had called unsinkable. One woman remains missing.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/23/rescuers-recover-fifth-body-from-sunken-superyacht-off-sicily-1-still-missing/"  >(Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 04:55:11 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 23 Aug 2024 04:55:11 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="BABAR DOGAR, Associated Press, PIX 11">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/23/attackers-ambush-and-kill-11-police-officers-in-eastern-pakistan-officials-say.webp" alt="Gunmen ambush and kill 11 police officers in eastern Pakistan, officials say" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Gunmen ambush and kill 11 police officers in eastern Pakistan, officials say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      LAHORE, Pakistan (AP) — Gunmen armed with rocket-propelled grenades ambushed a police convoy in eastern Punjab province on Thursday, killing at least 11 officers and wounding seven others, authorities said. No one immediately claimed responsibility for the attack in the Rahim Yar Khan district.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/23/attackers-ambush-and-kill-11-police-officers-in-eastern-pakistan-officials-say/"  >(BABAR DOGAR, Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:51:27 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:51:27 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Anna Kutz, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/16/israel-hamas-iran-john-bolton.webp" alt="John Bolton on Israel-Hamas cease-fire talks, Iranian tensions" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">John Bolton on Israel-Hamas cease-fire talks, Iranian tensions</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Bolton said Israel and Hamas have different definitions of "cease-fire" and are likely still "far apart" on a deal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/16/israel-hamas-iran-john-bolton/"  >(Anna Kutz, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/tech/">Technology</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:00:00 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Info World">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/08/19/how-to-bring-runaway-cloud-costs-under-control.webp" alt="How to bring runaway cloud costs under control" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How to bring runaway cloud costs under control</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      It’s no secret that organizations are deploying more and more cloud services as they look for ways to increase business agility and scalability while reducing costs. But in an interesting twist, increased cloud adoption can lead to runaway spending.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/19/how-to-bring-runaway-cloud-costs-under-control/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
