    <h3 itemprop="headline">San Diego mayor, congressional reps head to Chicago for DNC</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Democratic National Convention gets underway on Monday and San Diego's delegates, including some elected officials, are in Chicago for the weeklong event.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/san-diego-mayor-congressional-reps-head-to-chicago-for-dnc/"  >(Danielle Dawson, Fox 5)</a>
