    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former U.S. Rep. George Santos pleads guilty to wire fraud, identity theft</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      CENTRAL ISLIP, N.Y. (AP) — Former U.S. Rep. George Santos pleaded guilty Monday to wire fraud and aggravated identity theft, short-circuiting the federal fraud case that led to his expulsion from Congress just weeks before it was set to go to trial.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/former-u-s-rep-george-santos-pleads-guilty-to-wire-fraud-identity-theft/"  >(Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
