  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/19/dems-look-to-honor-biden-build-momentum-at-night-1-of-dnc.webp" alt="Day 1 of DNC wraps with Biden giving Harris an enthusiastic endorsement" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Day 1 of DNC wraps with Biden giving Harris an enthusiastic endorsement</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Following a hasty rebranding effort, Democrats open their 2024 Convention in Chicago on Monday riding a tide of momentum that has completely reshaped the party's prospects for retaining the White House for the next four years.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/dems-look-to-honor-biden-build-momentum-at-night-1-of-dnc/"  >(Bill Disbrow, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:02:06 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 19 Aug 2024 22:02:06 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rebecca Beitsch, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/19/fbi-concludes-iran-was-behind-trump-campaign-hack.webp" alt="FBI concludes Iran was behind Trump campaign hack" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">FBI concludes Iran was behind Trump campaign hack</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The FBI, alongside other intelligence agencies, announced Monday it concluded Iran was behind the hacking of the Trump campaign and that the country has attempted to disrupt both presidential campaigns.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/fbi-concludes-iran-was-behind-trump-campaign-hack/"  >(Rebecca Beitsch, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
